Commentary Text: Tushar Deshpande to Manish Pandey, out Caught by Dwayne Bravo!! Ah he has thrown it away. Not expected from such an experienced player. Slot ball, in Pandey's defence he saw this as an opportunity to power it high over the infield as mid-off is in. But he went too hard on the shot and never got elevation. Could have focused a bit more on lofting the ball than hitting it hard. Bravo waits at mid-off and catches this overhead so easily and does his dance moves. Two quick wickets for CSK. Manish Pandey c Dwayne Bravo b Tushar Deshpande 5(6)

Commentary Text: Pretorius to Rahul, out Caught by Rayudu!! Pretorious! What an end over specialist he has turned out to be. Short slower delivery outside off stump, Rahul knees down to pull, realizes pace was taken off, yet goes through. Gets a thick top edge that threatens to clear short fine leg. Rayudu does so well to run back, yet keep his eyes on the ball and stretch both hands to grab it cleanly. Made a difficult catch look simple. CSK finally get the wicket. Rahul c Rayudu b Pretorius 40(26) [4s-2 6s-3]
